2	
3	Mirrors nba_playoff/visualization/plots.py adapted for a FIFA World Cup
4	single-elimination bracket:
5	- No best-of-7 series — each tie is a single match.
6	- No conferences — all slots flow left-to-right toward the Final.
7	- Teams are country-name strings.
8	- RoundResult is accepted duck-typed (not imported at module level) so that
9	  the simulation package can be developed in parallel without creating a
10	  circular dependency.  The contract expected from each RoundResult value:
11	      .round_num: int
12	      .probabilities: dict[str, float]   (team -> advancement probability)
13	"""
